dct_title_s: Map of property belonging to the German Transatlantic Co. of the City of Danbury
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Hudson Street to the Hudson River in Hoboken City. Map shows the property of the German Transatlantic Steam Navigation Co. as well as that of Henry Otto. Map also shows the exterior line of piers and the exterior line of solid filling.
